V0106_01_00_00_0.text: I knew we'd Duel eventually. Because the best must face the best!

V0106_01_00_00_1.text: Let's see what you can do!

V0106_01_00_01_0.text: I'll give this Duel my all.

V0106_01_00_02_0.text:
Let's Duel, Jaden!
I've always wanted a rematch!

V0106_01_00_03_0.text: Why are you always hanging around me?

V0106_01_00_03_1.text:
If it's because you want to Duel, just say so.
Don't be such a creeper!

V0106_01_00_06_1.text: I'll make you come to your senses!

V0106_03_00_00_0.text: You're getting no mercy from me!

V0106_05_00_00_0.text:
Just like you, I can't lose!
Because I also have something worth fighting for!

V0106_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0106_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Mystical Space Typhoon!

V0106_08_00_01_0.text: I activate my Quick-Play Spell, Scapegoat!

V0106_08_00_01_1.text: I Special Summon 4 Sheep Tokens in Defense Position!

V0106_08_00_02_0.text:
My Trap Card activates!
Doble Passe!

V0106_08_00_02_1.text:
As a Duelist, I'll do everything it takes to win!
Even if that means taking damage!

V0106_08_00_05_0.text: I activate my Trap Card, Hallowed Life Barrier!

V0106_08_00_07_0.text:
My Continuous Trap activates!
Call of the Haunted!

V0106_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Machine Angel Ritual!

V0106_08_00_10_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Pot of Greed!

V0106_08_00_10_1.text: I draw two cards from my Deck!

V0106_08_00_11_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Fulfillment of the Contract!

V0106_08_00_12_0.text: In a Duel, I always give it my all!

V0106_08_00_12_1.text: I'll change the scenery by activating the Field Spell, Ritual Sanctuary!

V0106_08_00_13_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, The Warrior Returning Alive!

V0106_08_00_14_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Stray Lambs!

V0106_08_00_14_1.text: I Special Summon two Lamb Tokens on my field!

V0106_08_00_15_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Polymerization!

V0106_08_00_16_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Fusion Recovery!

V0106_08_00_17_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, <card mrk=6849/>!

V0106_08_00_18_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, White Veil!

V0106_08_00_19_0.text: I activate my Continuous Trap, Limit Reverse!

V0106_08_00_20_0.text: I activate Machine Angel Absolute Ritual!

V0106_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0106_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0106_13_00_02_0.text:
This card is just what I need!
Cold Enchanter!

V0106_13_00_03_0.text: Come on out, Cyber Angel Benten!

V0106_13_00_07_0.text: Cyber Tutu, dance to the stage!

V0106_13_00_08_0.text: Flutter to the field, Cyber Petit Angel!

V0106_13_00_10_0.text: A true star never avoids the spotlight!

V0106_13_00_14_0.text: The freezing conqueror of all the lands arrives!

V0106_13_00_16_0.text:
This monster will let me see all your strategies!
Mind on Air!

V0106_13_00_18_0.text: My beautiful angel shall heal the world!

V0106_13_00_19_0.text: Light up the world with your eternal power!

V0106_16_00_00_0.text: It's the end of the line!

V0106_18_00_01_0.text: I attack you directly with my monster!

V0106_19_00_04_0.text:
Here I go!
I attack with Cyber Angel Dakini!

V0106_19_00_05_0.text:
Here I go!
I attack with Cyber Angel Idaten!

V0106_19_00_11_0.text: Blizzard Dragon! Turn 'em into an ice cube!

V0106_28_00_00_0.text:
I wish you took this Duel seriously.
I don't have time to be playing around!

V0106_28_00_01_0.text: Don't get me wrong - I'm glad that I won, but I can't get too overconfident.

V0106_28_00_02_0.text: You have to give it your all, from building the best Deck to making the right moves.

V0106_28_00_02_1.text: When you're ready to do that, I'll take you on again!

V0106_28_00_03_1.text: There's never a dull moment when I'm Dueling against you.

V0106_28_00_04_0.text:
Sorry, Chazz-anova.
Wanna know who I love?

V0106_29_00_00_0.text: Making the right moves at the right time... You have the instincts to be a champ!

V0106_29_00_01_1.text: Nicely done! But I won't lose in our rematch!

V0106_29_00_02_0.text:
Argh...
I didn't know there were Duelists as strong as you.

V0106_29_00_03_1.text: Jaden, you never cease to surprise me. But I'll surprise you next time!

V0106_29_00_04_1.text: He's out of it. I wonder what he's thinking about.

V0106_33_00_00_0.text: A Duelist never gives less than 100%!

V0106_33_00_01_0.text: I'll show you why I Duel!

V0106_34_00_01_0.text: Wait a sec! What's with that!

V0106_34_00_03_0.text: You do realize you can't win, right?

V0106_34_00_04_0.text: I'll send chills down your spine!

V0106_34_00_06_0.text: Maybe you should take this Duel seriously.

V0106_34_00_07_0.text: I expected a tough Duel. I guess I was wrong.

V0106_27_00_00_0.text: It's not over! I know I can still win!
